Symbol.Script_3D:
! Gen Tank ! Zsolt Feke
PEN gs_cont_pen MATERIAL tankMat RESOL res
IF typ = 1 THEN chRad = endRed tankRad = tankDia/2 sNum = MAX(INT(res/6), 2) alpha_i = 90/sNum
PUT 0, 0, 1 alpha = 0 FOR i=1 TO sNum+1 PUT chRad-chRad*COS(alpha), tankRad-chRad+chRad*SIN(alpha), 1-1*(i=1 OR i=sNum+1) alpha = alpha+alpha_i NEXT i
alpha = 0 FOR i=1 TO sNum+1 PUT tankLen-chRad+chRad*SIN(alpha), tankRad-chRad+chRad*COS(alpha), 1-1*(i=1 OR i=sNum+1) alpha = alpha+alpha_i NEXT i
PUT tankLen, 0, 1
ROTy -90*tankPos REVOLVE NSP/3, 360, 4+8,
GET (NSP)
IF ringOn THEN FOR i = 1 TO 2 ADDx ring_AxisPos+(tankLen-ring_AxisPos*2-ringWidth)*(i=2) ROTy 90 PRISM_ 4, ringWidth, 0, 0, 979, tankRad+ringThick, 360, 4079, 0, 0, 979, tankRad, 360, 4079 DEL 2 NEXT i ENDIF DEL 1 ENDIF
IF typ = 2 THEN tankRad = tankDia/2 alphaTankEnd = (180-2*ATN(tankRad/endRed)) Rad = tankRad/SIN(alphaTankEnd)
sNum = MAX(INT(res/6), 2) alpha_i = alphaTankEnd/sNum
PUT 0, 0, 1
alpha = 0 FOR i=1 TO sNum+1 PUT Rad-Rad*COS(alpha), Rad*SIN(alpha), 1-1*(i=sNum+1) alpha = alpha+alpha_i NEXT i
alpha = 0 FOR i=1 TO sNum+1 PUT tankLen-Rad+Rad*COS(alphaTankEnd-alpha), Rad*SIN(alphaTankEnd-alpha), 1-1*(i=1) alpha = alpha+alpha_i NEXT i
ROTy -90*tankPos REVOLVE NSP/3, 360, 4+8,
GET (NSP)
IF ringOn THEN FOR i = 1 TO 2 ADDx ring_AxisPos+(tankLen-ring_AxisPos*2-ringWidth)*(i=2) ROTy 90 PRISM_ 4, ringWidth, 0, 0, 979, tankRad+ringThick, 360, 4079, 0, 0, 979, tankRad, 360, 4079 DEL 2 NEXT i ENDIF DEL 1 ENDIF
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Gen Tank ! Zsolt Feke
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = hptsID IF typ = 1 THEN chRad = endRed tankRad = tankDia/2
IF tankPos THEN
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
POLY2_B 2, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 901, tankRad+ringThick*ringOn, 360, 4001
IF ringOn THEN CIRCLE2 0, 0, tankRad CIRCLE2 0, 0, tankRad-chRad ENDIF
ELSE
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 tankLen, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
PUT 0, -(tankRad-chRad), 1 PUT 0, tankRad-chRad, 1 PUT chRad, tankRad, 1001
IF ringOn = 1 THEN HOTSPOT2 ring_AxisPos+ringWidth/2, tankRad+ringThick, unID: unID=unID+1 LINE2 ring_AxisPos, tankRad, ring_AxisPos, -tankRad LINE2 ring_AxisPos+ringWidth, tankRad, ring_AxisPos+ringWidth, -tankRad PUT ring_AxisPos, tankRad, 1 PUT ring_AxisPos, tankRad+ringThick, 1 PUT ring_AxisPos+ringWidth, tankRad+ringThick, 1 PUT ring_AxisPos+ringWidth, tankRad, 1
HOTSPOT2 tankLen-ring_AxisPos-ringWidth/2, tankRad+ringThick, unID: unID=unID+1 LINE2 tankLen-ring_AxisPos-ringWidth, tankRad, tankLen-ring_AxisPos-ringWidth, -tankRad LINE2 tankLen-ring_AxisPos, tankRad, tankLen-ring_AxisPos, -tankRad PUT tankLen-ring_AxisPos-ringWidth, tankRad, 1 PUT tankLen-ring_AxisPos-ringWidth, tankRad+ringThick, 1 PUT tankLen-ring_AxisPos, tankRad+ringThick, 1 PUT tankLen-ring_AxisPos, tankRad, 1 ENDIF
PUT tankLen-chRad, tankRad, 1 PUT tankLen-chRad, tankRad-chRad, 901 PUT tankLen, tankRad-chRad, 3001 PUT tankLen, -(tankRad-chRad), 1 PUT tankLen-chRad, -tankRad, 1001
IF ringOn = 1 THEN HOTSPOT2 tankLen-ring_AxisPos-ringWidth/2, -tankRad-ringThick, unID: unID=unID+1 PUT tankLen-ring_AxisPos, -tankRad, 1 PUT tankLen-ring_AxisPos, -tankRad-ringThick, 1 PUT tankLen-ring_AxisPos-ringWidth, -tankRad-ringThick, 1 PUT tankLen-ring_AxisPos-ringWidth, -tankRad, 1
HOTSPOT2 ring_AxisPos+ringWidth/2, -tankRad-ringThick, unID: unID=unID+1 PUT ring_AxisPos+ringWidth, -tankRad, 1 PUT ring_AxisPos+ringWidth, -tankRad-ringThick, 1 PUT ring_AxisPos, -tankRad-ringThick, 1 PUT ring_AxisPos, -tankRad, 1 ENDIF
PUT chRad, -tankRad, 1 PUT chRad, -(tankRad-chRad), 901 PUT 0, -(tankRad-chRad), 3001
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP) ENDIF ENDIF
IF typ = 2 THEN tankRad = tankDia/2 alphaTankEnd = (180-2*ATN(tankRad/endRed)) Rad = tankRad/SIN(alphaTankEnd)
IF tankPos THEN
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
POLY2_B 2, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 901, tankRad, 360, 4001
IF ringOn THEN POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 901, tankRad+ringThick, 360, 4001, 0, 0, 901, tankRad, 360, 4001 ENDIF
ELSE
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 tankLen, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
PUT endRed, -tankRad, 1 PUT Rad, 0, 901 PUT endRed, tankRad, 3001
IF ringOn = 1 THEN HOTSPOT2 ring_AxisPos+ringWidth/2, tankRad+ringThick, unID: unID=unID+1 LINE2 ring_AxisPos, tankRad, ring_AxisPos, -tankRad LINE2 ring_AxisPos+ringWidth, tankRad, ring_AxisPos+ringWidth, -tankRad PUT ring_AxisPos, tankRad, 1 PUT ring_AxisPos, tankRad+ringThick, 1 PUT ring_AxisPos+ringWidth, tankRad+ringThick, 1 PUT ring_AxisPos+ringWidth, tankRad, 1
HOTSPOT2 tankLen-ring_AxisPos-ringWidth/2, tankRad+ringThick, unID: unID=unID+1 LINE2 tankLen-ring_AxisPos-ringWidth, tankRad, tankLen-ring_AxisPos-ringWidth, -tankRad LINE2 tankLen-ring_AxisPos, tankRad, tankLen-ring_AxisPos, -tankRad PUT tankLen-ring_AxisPos-ringWidth, tankRad, 1 PUT tankLen-ring_AxisPos-ringWidth, tankRad+ringThick, 1 PUT tankLen-ring_AxisPos, tankRad+ringThick, 1 PUT tankLen-ring_AxisPos, tankRad, 1 ENDIF
PUT tankLen-endRed, tankRad, 1 PUT tankLen-Rad, 0, 901 PUT tankLen-endRed, -tankRad, 3001
IF ringOn = 1 THEN HOTSPOT2 tankLen-ring_AxisPos-ringWidth/2, -tankRad-ringThick, unID: unID=unID+1 PUT tankLen-ring_AxisPos, -tankRad, 1 PUT tankLen-ring_AxisPos, -tankRad-ringThick, 1 PUT tankLen-ring_AxisPos-ringWidth, -tankRad-ringThick, 1 PUT tankLen-ring_AxisPos-ringWidth, -tankRad, 1
HOTSPOT2 ring_AxisPos+ringWidth/2, -tankRad-ringThick, unID: unID=unID+1 PUT ring_AxisPos+ringWidth, -tankRad, 1 PUT ring_AxisPos+ringWidth, -tankRad-ringThick, 1 PUT ring_AxisPos, -tankRad-ringThick, 1 PUT ring_AxisPos, -tankRad, 1 ENDIF
PUT endRed, -tankRad, -1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP) ENDIF ENDIF
